$ Header --------------------------------------------
PROJECT 'Stationary case for San Andres' '1'
'Example'
$
$ Computational mesh -----------------------------------
SET NAUT
MODE STAT TWOD
COORD SPHE CCM
CGRID REG 278.2265167 12.4413166 0 0.13185 0.1908 293 424 CIRCLE 72 0.04 1
$
$ Bathymetry --------------------------------------------
INP BOT REG 278.2265167 12.4413166 0 293 424 0.00045 0.00045 EXC -9999.
READ BOT 1 'bathy_file.bot' 1 FREE
$
$ Bottom friction ---------------------------------------

$
$ Wind --------------------------------------------------
WIND 12.8 90
$
$ Condiciones iniciales----------------------------------
INIT DEF
$
$ Condiciones de frontera -------------------------------
BOU SHAP JON PEAK
$
BOU SIDE segment_dir CLOCKW CON values_bounds
$
$ Parametros fisicos y numericos ------------------------
GEN3 JANS 9 1
QUAD
TRI
BRE
FRIC MAD
DIFFR
$ Numerics -----------------------------------
PROP BSBT
NUM STOPC 0 0.01 0.001 101 STAT mxitst=120
NUM CT 0.4
$
$ Resultados ---------------------------------------------
$  -> Campos de oleaje
BLOCK 'COMPGRID' NOHEAD 'wave_field.mat' LAY 3 HSIGN TPS TM01 DIR
$
$ Final --------------------------------------------------
TEST 1, 0
COMP 
STOP